@host = http://localhost:3000

### Get user balance
GET {{host}}/users/b2c3d4e5-f6a7-4901-bcde-f12345678901/balance

### Get balance — non-existent user (should return 404)
GET {{host}}/users/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000/balance

### Get balance — invalid UUID (should return 400)
GET {{host}}/users/not-a-uuid/balance
